""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

INNER JOIN (

    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]

        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]

        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY

) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]

    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
